Package oopds.assignment.DC.services

Class DonationDistributedService

java.lang.Object
oopds.assignment.DC.services.DonationDistributedService
@Service public class DonationDistributedService extends Object
A Service Class to be used by the Spring API to do certain operations based on the method called. This service class contains the operations that involves the DonationDistributed.
